# PetHive - Frameworks & Technologies

| Feature | Technology |
|---------|-----------|
| Real-time UI updates | React + Framer Motion |
| Routing & Navigation | React Router DOM |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS |
| API Communication | Axios |
| Backend API | Express + CORS |
| Data Persistence | Prisma + SQLite/PostgreSQL |
| Authentication | Google Auth + BCryptjs |
| Session Management | Cookie Session |
| Development | Vite + Nodemon |
| Documentation/Markdown | React Markdown + Remark GFM |